O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:6:"page_1";s:840:"<p>Whether you want to add a detailed products and services page to your small business website or just need to publish up a quick blog post, Upfront lets you create posts and pages with ease from the front-end of your site.</p>
<p>No longer do you have to create pages in the backend of your site, not really knowing how it's going to look once published. With Upfront, you can create pages and posts and see how they will look on your site as you make edits. It really couldn't be any simpler!</p>
<p>Likewise, Upfront also provides a straightforward interface for responsive design so you can rearrange the content on your site so that it looks fantastic on any device.</p>
<p>In this tutorial, you’ll learn how to create and edit pages and posts, and how to use Upfront's simple responsive design interface.</p>
<p>Let's jump in!</p>
